{%- comment -%}
  /**
   * CUSTOM SLIDESHOW SECTION
   *
   * A comprehensive and responsive slideshow component that displays promotional content
   * in an interactive carousel format. This section supports multiple layout configurations,
   * multi-language content, and advanced customization options for creating engaging
   * hero banners and promotional displays.
   *
   * CORE FEATURES:
   * - Multi-layout slideshow with 4 layout options (image-right, image-left, image-top, image-bottom)
   * - Auto-playing carousel with manual navigation controls
   * - Multi-language support (English, German, French, Finnish)
   * - Customizable sales tags with localized content
   * - Responsive design with mobile-optimized layouts
   * - Touch/swipe navigation for mobile devices
   * - Pagination dots and arrow navigation
   * - Customizable typography and color schemes
   * - Background color customization per slide
   *
   * TECHNICAL IMPLEMENTATION:
   * - CSS-based slide transitions with opacity animations
   * - JavaScript-powered carousel functionality with autoplay
   * - Responsive image handling with srcset and WebP format support
   * - Mobile-first responsive design with breakpoint at 768px
   * - CSS Grid and Flexbox layouts for different screen sizes
   * - Touch event handling for mobile swipe gestures
   *
   * SHOPIFY INTEGRATION:
   * - Shopify Liquid templating with block-based architecture
   * - Image picker integration with Shopify's image transformation API
   * - Multi-language locale detection and content switching
   * - URL picker for button links with Shopify URL handling
   * - Rich text editor support for descriptions
   * - Color picker integration for styling customization
   *
   * RELATED FILES:
   *
   * Core Section File:
   * - sections/custom-slideshow.liquid - This main section file
   *
   * Layout Dependencies:
   * - layout/theme.liquid - Main theme layout with global settings and scripts
   *
   * RESPONSIVE BREAKPOINTS:
   * - Desktop (769px+): Full carousel functionality with navigation controls
   * - Mobile (768px-): Stacked layout with disabled navigation, vertical scrolling
   *
   * LAYOUT CONFIGURATIONS:
   * - image-right: Text content on left, image on right (default)
   * - image-left: Image on left, text content on right
   * - image-top: Image above text content
   * - image-bottom: Text content above image
   *
   * BROWSER COMPATIBILITY:
   * - Modern browsers with CSS Grid and Flexbox support
   * - Touch device support for mobile navigation
   * - Progressive enhancement for older browsers
   * - WebP image format support with fallbacks
   *
   * PERFORMANCE CONSIDERATIONS:
   * - Lazy loading support for slide images
   * - WebP format optimization for faster loading
   * - Responsive image srcset for optimal bandwidth usage
   * - Hardware-accelerated CSS transitions
   * - Efficient JavaScript with event delegation
   * - Automatic cleanup of event listeners on resize
   *
   * ACCESSIBILITY:
   * - Semantic HTML structure with proper heading hierarchy
   * - Alt text support for all images
   * - Keyboard navigation support for controls
   * - Focus management for interactive elements
   * - Screen reader friendly content structure
   *
   * CUSTOMIZATION OPTIONS:
   * - Unlimited slides with individual configuration
   * - Layout selection per slide
   * - Background color customization per slide
   * - Typography controls (font size, weight, color)
   * - Mobile-specific font size settings
   * - Button styling (text color, background color)
   * - Sales tag configuration with multi-language support
   * - Image upload and positioning
   * - Link destination configuration
   *
   * AUTOPLAY FUNCTIONALITY:
   * - 5-second interval between slides
   * - Automatic pause on user interaction
   * - Resume autoplay after user interaction
   * - Disabled on mobile devices for better UX
   *
   * USAGE SCENARIOS:
   * - Homepage hero banners
   * - Product promotional displays
   * - Seasonal campaign showcases
   * - Multi-product feature highlights
   * - Brand storytelling presentations
   */
